            "text": "<p>At ThePlaygroundStore.com, we know that securing funding can be one of the biggest challenges of any project. The reality is, playgrounds involve more than just the cost of the equipment. Expenses like shipping, installation, and surfacing are often overlooked but are essential costs that cannot be avoided.<\/p>"
