    "video_plus_text_rna3Xc": {
      "type": "video-plus-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_kyQwPd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text_content_header": "Financing",
            "text_content": "<p>If you're working with a limited budget and need to spread out the costs of your project, financing is an ideal solution! With financing, you can build your playground in stages, adding equipment incrementally and paying for each phase as it’s completed. In as few as 3-5 phases, you can have the playground of your dreams.<\/p><p><br\/>Benefits Of Financing include:<\/p><ul><li>Flexibility that allows you to pay as you go<\/li><li>Affordable options that don't stretch your budget too thin<\/li><li>New features are added to your playground each year<\/li><\/ul>",
            "text-alignment": "center",
            "background": "#ffffff"
          }
        }
      },
